headline: Mizuho Maintains Outperform on Quest Diagnostics, Raises Price Target to $235
summary: Mizuho  analyst Ann Hynes   maintains Quest Diagnostics (NYSE:DGX) with a Outperform and raises the price target from $210 to $235.
